      <title>美联储调查显示美国银行报告贷款需求疲软</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-banks-report-weaker-loan-demand-fed-survey-says-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据美联储周一公布的对高级信贷官员的调查，美国各银行报告今年第一季度工业贷款需求再次疲软，家庭信贷需求下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-banks-report-weaker-loan-demand-fed-survey-says-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 19:33:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
